


// CartService
 - properties
   Cart

 - methods

    viewCart
    ---------
    > if (cart has something)
        Do ( print Item and Quantity from HashMap)
      else Do ( print 'No items currently in your cart')

    addItem(Item)
    ------------
    > show available inventory of items as numbered menu
    > user first enters int for item and then an int for quantity desired
        - checks to make sure quantity entered is > than quantity available
    > reduces inventory by quantity entered
    > adds item / quantity to Cart Map

   removeItem
   ----------
   > asks user what item they want to remove after showing the current cart state
   > gives user the prompt to enter name of item
   > checks for valid name
        - if valid removes item from cart
   > updates cart and inventory

   checkoutCart
   ------------
   > Confirms with user they want to checkout cart
    - mini menu with yes / no
   > Displays the total item in cart and the cost
   > Users selects to confirm purchase
    - mini menu with yes / no
   > Shows checkout successful
   > Cart is emptied and user goes back to main menu


// Cart
  - properties
    Item, quantity, HashMap



// Inventory
  - properties
    ArrayList Item
    quantity


// Item
   - properties
     itemName, itemPrice
     getter / setters